issue.message: WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE no longer provides write access when targeting Android 10, unless you use `requestLegacyExternalStorage`

Call requires API level 35 (current min is 21): `java.util.List#removeFirst` (Prior to API level 35, this call would resolve to a Kotlin stdlib extension function. You can use `remove(`*index*`)` instead.)
Avoid passing `null` as the view root (needed to resolve layout parameters on the inflated layout's root element)
A newer version of org.jetbrains.kotlin:kotlin-stdlib-jdk7 than 2.0.21 is available: 2.2.0
